<p class="ql-align-justify">5：Hisilicon- Hi6365-射频收发芯片</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">6：Murata-多路调制器芯片</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">7：Hisilicon-Hi6H12-低噪声放大器芯片</p>
